  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A Food Frequency Questionnaire (FFQ), will be provided to 800 adults to assess overall
      fructose intake and this will be related to a number of features related to the metabolic
      syndrome, including serum leptin, characteristic features of metabolic syndrome (body mass
      index, waist circumference, plasma lipids, blood pressure, HOMA index,fasting glucose and
      fasting insulin levels) and other as: CRP, fibrinogen, homocysteine and uric acid.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
